{"tid":160970,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有愛 幫幫幾隻流浪狗","createTime":"2017-03-18T08:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T14:40:36.000Z","uid":5489,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd99d989a4b54a9334e002f375ecab6f72a5b996","tid":160970,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"連登有愛<br />\n之前我都係度出過post 講佢地<br />\n最近佢地病得好嚴重<br />\nFacebook 出現左佢地既求救post <br />\n希望幫到佢地搵到組織肯醫又好<br />\n暫托又好 領養都好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求下巴絲幫手大力share <br />\n<br />\nFacebook 原文：<br />\n急求幫忙   救救五隻被遺棄有花柳病嘅浪浪<br />\n<br />\n🐶🐶的話 : <br />\n我係四隻有大有細浪浪嘅大佬， 每日由朝到晚看守著一個地盤 。<br />\n我哋平時肚餓，就會食地盤工人俾我哋既飯盒。<br />\n有時冇人餵，我哋就會捉地盤啲老鼠食。<br />\n曾經係一年前，有漁農署既叔叔黎捉左我哋6個朋友，雖然捉我哋唔到，但我哋開始變得好怕人。<br />\n<br />\n平時有人行近，都會俾我哋吠走，但係有個哥哥竟然吠極都唔走，仲每日黎餵我哋，我哋開始覺得人類都唔係咁可怕。<br />\n<br />\n可惜，唔知幾時開始我哋行動慢左 ，下體好痛好痛， 仲有少少流血。不過就算係咁 我都要保護我一家人。就算再痛 ，成臉傷痕，我都會打敗入侵者，保護家園。 <br />\n<br />\n哥哥好想幫我哋，但係因為佢仲讀緊書，所以帶唔到我哋走。佢試過周圍搵人幫手，但係都係冇好消息。<br />\n期間，花花曾經俾其他人發現，仲有人黎捉佢。但係咁多陌生人出現，我哋都好驚，佢捉我哋唔到，而我哋都變得更加怕人。<br />\n<br />\n日復日，最近我哋嘅病愈黎愈嚴重，一路行一路流血，周圍都見到我哋嘅血跡，下體仲不停滴血 ，又腫又紅又佈滿血絲 。我哋開始追趕不上其他狗狗 。<br />\n<br />\n我聽到哥哥講，我地可能染上左性病，會傳染。性病喺乜，會好痛？會流血？會潰爛 ，會死嗎？<br />\n<br />\n哥哥冇放棄，仲搵左附近嘅姨姨一齊幫手。終於，我哋決定再信哥哥一次，每晚都跟佢行去一條倔頭路食嘢，等左咁耐，哥哥終於有機會可以捉到我哋喇。有人可以伸出援手嗎？<br />\n<br />\n五隻永遠忠心主人的浪浪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/mongrelclub.hk/permalink/1343662342338788/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fmongrelclub.hk%2Fpermalink%2F1343662342338788%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=57614635\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/mongrelclub.hk/permalink/1343662342338788/</a>"},{"pid":"cf8d9b60c3ba1de2354cbee57719adb688896315","tid":160970,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d933c7f2cf7c6a226d749082c5f555d1474a96e","tid":160970,"uid":15580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:09:18.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bc89767b7ee3fef961f30b4ef2082654badeb9","tid":160970,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"前post：<br />\n今晚氣溫12度 5隻狗已經得返1隻... <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/58202/page/9?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/58202/page/9?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n冇斷手斷腳<br />\n冇噴血爆肚<br />\n冇noise 冇話題性<br />\n但有病就係有病<br />\n會感染會死<br />\n唔通連流浪狗都要鬥慘？"},{"pid":"1a8da10959b197dc433565576a76fa315333523c","tid":160970,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d384eaad4c59befc4ad2a9373b5de43936e07fec","tid":160970,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90c675ce6b6d12f5042bbaa40e68e444d457995","tid":160970,"uid":24780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449173d2e95aa9b9121409caf115be607e00141c","tid":160970,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:48:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268501e987d802d991b22aabf77a744ac0f91b13","tid":160970,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dis